#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "आमुख"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmix; supports several platforms and sound drivers."
msgstr "&kmix; अनेकमञ्चान् ध्वनिचालकान् च समर्थयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have both ALSA and Open Sound System drivers installed, &kmix; will "
"use the ALSA driver."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवतां कृते ALSA तथा Open Sound System चालकद्वयं संस्थापितम् अस्ति तर्हि &kmix; "
"ALSA चालकस्य उपयोगं करिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:92 index.docbook:113
